OL,3,CTeenage driver who seriously injured
OL,4,Cboy, 4, in hit-and-run sentenced
OL,6,FA teenage driver has been sentenced
OL,7,Ffor causing a crash which nearly
OL,8,Fkilled a four-year-old who was waiting
OL,9,Ffor a bus.
OL,11,FBristol Crown Court heard James
OL,12,FDoherty, 18, had only bought the BMW
OL,13,F45 minutes before the collision in
OL,14,FLawrence Weston, Bristol in November
OL,15,F2024.
OL,17,FThe boy suffered spinal, rib and
OL,18,Fpelvic fractures as well as internal
OL,19,Fbleeding. The court heard he has since
OL,20,Fgone blind and requires a wheelchair.
