OL,3,CTeenage driver who seriously injured
OL,4,Cboy, 4, in hit-and-run sentenced
OL,6,FAt a hearing at Bristol Crown Court,
OL,7,FDoherty pleaded guilty to causing
OL,8,Fserious injury by dangerous driving.
OL,10,FThe court heard how Doherty drove
OL,11,Fround a corner in the Lawrence Weston
OL,12,Farea of Bristol too fast at about 2pm
OL,13,Fon 17 November last year.
OL,15,FDoherty's car crashed straight into a
OL,16,Fbus stop where a four-year-old boy,
OL,17,Fwho cannot be named for legal reasons,
OL,18,Fwas waiting with his father and
OL,19,Fstepmother.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/12
