OL,3,CTeenage driver who seriously injured
OL,4,Cboy, 4, in hit-and-run sentenced
OL,6,FIn a victim impact statement, the
OL,7,Fboy's father said his "whole world
OL,8,Fcame crashing down" when he saw the
OL,9,Fcar hit his son.
OL,11,FHe told the court how he still has
OL,12,Fflashbacks and cannot cross the road.
OL,13,FThe boy spent "weeks in hospital
OL,14,Ffighting for his life", his father
OL,15,Fexplained.
OL,17,F"The accident not only devastated his
OL,18,Fbody ` it has robbed him of his
OL,19,Fchildhood. Our boy cannot do the
OL,20,Fthings a normal boy can do.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/12
