OL,3,CTeenage driver who seriously injured
OL,4,Cboy, 4, in hit-and-run sentenced
OL,6,F"This is heartbreaking. Our children
OL,7,Fhave had their brother ripped away
OL,8,Fweeks before Christmas.
OL,10,F"He lost first few days of his baby
OL,11,Fbrother and the tragedy has affected
OL,12,Fthe whole family. Emotionally we are
OL,13,Fshattered and broken. We have had to
OL,14,Fgive up our jobs to care for him.
OL,16,F"It was the moment our son's bright
OL,17,Ffuture was stolen from him."
OL,19,FThe boy's stepmother added that the
OL,20,Flast few months had been "torture".
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/12
