OL,6,F"When I checked the bus was going to
OL,7,Farrive in three minutes ` my life and
OL,8,Fmy stepson's life changed in that
OL,9,Fthree minutes," she said.
OL,11,FJudge's remarks on sentencing
OL,13,FJudge Peter Blair, the Recorder of
OL,14,FBristol, described Doherty as an
OL,15,F"idiot" who had exhibited "terrible
OL,16,Fdriving" during the incident.
