OL,4,Cboy, 4, in hit-and-run sentenced
OL,6,FThe judge sentenced Doherty to two
OL,7,Fyears and two months in a young
OL,8,Foffenders' institute and banned him
OL,9,Ffrom driving for four years and one
OL,10,Fmonth.
OL,12,FHe told Doherty: "On Sunday November
OL,13,F17, a very short while after you had
OL,14,Farrived in England with your wife, you
OL,15,Fused some savings and family help to
OL,16,Fpurchase yourselves a motor car.
OL,26,@tD@ROU
