OL,3,CTeenage driver who seriously injured
OL,4,Cboy, 4, in hit-and-run sentenced
OL,6,F"You picked it up that Sunday morning.
OL,7,FWithin a very short time with it being
OL,8,Fin your ownership, you drove at a
OL,9,Fspeed that was totally inappropriate
OL,10,Ffor the conditions. Your wife, who is
OL,11,Fpregnant, was in that vehicle with you.
OL,13,F"When you came round that corner, the
OL,14,Frear of the vehicle that you had just
OL,15,Facquired swung out. You countered that
OL,16,Fin an inappropriate way, which had you
OL,17,Fswinging the car right back across the
OL,18,Froad where there was a bus stop."
