OL,3,CTeenage driver who seriously injured
OL,4,Cboy, 4, in hit-and-run sentenced
OL,6,FThe judge described how the boy had
OL,7,Fbeen sitting at the bus stop with his
OL,8,Fstepmother, with his father nearby,
OL,9,Fand they were both struck by the car.
OL,11,FJudge Blair said: "That was
OL,12,Fextraordinarily culpable and utterly
OL,13,Fcowardly, for which you should rightly
OL,14,Ffeel incredible shame."
OL,16,FHe described how the boy had been left
OL,17,Fwith "terrible injuries" and it was
OL,18,Finitially feared he would not survive
OL,19,Fthe incident.
