OL,3,CTeenage driver who seriously injured
OL,4,Cboy, 4, in hit-and-run sentenced
OL,6,F"He, in fact, has survived but he has
OL,7,Fsuffered terribly in terms of pain
OL,8,Fthrough the treatment and the therapy
OL,9,Fthat is going to be required for him
OL,10,Ffor years," the judge said.
OL,12,FProsecuting, Kaj Scarsbrook played the
OL,13,Fcourt CCTV footage which showed the
OL,14,FBMW crashing into the bus stop and
OL,15,FDoherty fleeing the scene with his
OL,16,Fwife as members of the public ran to
OL,17,Fhelp.
OL,19,FMr Scarsbrook said the victim's
OL,20,Fstepmother sustained injuries to her
OL,21,Fleg.
