OL,6,FDoherty had traces of cannabis in his
OL,7,Fsystem when he was arrested after
OL,8,Fhanding himself in, Mr Scarsbrook said.
OL,10,FDoherty's barrister said his client,
OL,11,Fwho is from the Irish traveller
OL,12,Fcommunity, had moved to England with
OL,13,Fhis wife just one week before the
OL,14,Fincident. The couple are now expecting
OL,15,Fa baby, which is due to be born in
OL,16,FApril.
